---
title: Shawarma-Spiced Lamb Chops and Fig Sauce with Garlic-Herb Potatoes, Asparagus and Almonds
description: This dish is a perfect combination of flavours! A sweet fig sauce, garlicky herb roasted potatoes and zesty asparagus compliment the richness of the lamb chops.
